      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，知识库要有一个1b步骤，生成embeddings，目标是一个独立的患者记录数据库，叫HealthTech_PatientRecords。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Knowledge_Base",
        "HealthTech_PatientRecords",
        "Generate Embeddings"
