      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "了解，所以DiagnosticEngine到E是2a生成嵌入。然后E要去PatientRecords数据库做向量相似度搜索？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine",
