    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，4a和4b都是Combine，DiagnosticEngine自己和自己合并？不对，让我想想——应该是DiagnosticEngine的两个输出合并到P，P代表处理后的提示。",
